<section class="loyalty-rewards loyalty-rewards--coming-soon">
  <div class="loyalty-rewards__left">
    <p class="loyalty-eyebrow">Coming Soon</p>

    <h2>Farm Store Rewards are still growing.</h2>

    <p>
      The CPP Farm Store loyalty experience is being planned as part of the future
      omnichannel customer journey. Soon, shoppers could earn rewards for purchases,
      seasonal promotions, gift orders, and special Farm Store events.
    </p>

    <a href="/pages/visit-pickup-gift-order-faq" class="loyalty-btn">
      Learn About Store Pickup
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="loyalty-rewards__right">

    <div class="reward-card reward-card--soon">
      <span class="reward-card__label">Planned Feature</span>
      <h3>Earn Points</h3>
      <p>Future customers could earn points every time they shop online or in store.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reward-card reward-card--soon">
      <span class="reward-card__label">Omnichannel Idea</span>
      <h3>Pickup Rewards</h3>
      <p>Rewards could support online browsing, store pickup, and repeat Farm Store visits.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reward-card reward-card--soon">
      <span class="reward-card__label">Customer Experience</span>
      <h3>Seasonal Perks</h3>
      <p>Members could receive reminders for seasonal produce, gift boxes, and limited-time bundles.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

